### Issue description

I create a shader by follow code and attach to a sprite.
```glsl
shader_type canvas_item;

uniform float shake_intensity = 0.0;
uniform float shake_speed = 20.0;

void vertex() {
	vec2 shake = vec2(0.0);
	if (VERTEX.y < 0.0) {
		shake.x = sin(TIME * shake_speed + VERTEX.y) * shake_intensity;
	}
	VERTEX.xy += shake;
}
```

It works with different between  2D viewport and debug window,  the  shake_intensity  = 0.8 ,  shake_speed = 20， debug widow only shake toped of the sprited 2D. Even when shake_intensity <= 0.5 , it will not shake at debug window. 2D viewport works always well.

